      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WALTZING DIABLO (1) was quickly out of the tricky draw with a fast early sectional and clocked 19.15 with a half a length win at Healesville over 350m. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Great chance to get the job done again. TURTLE TIME (6) comes here off a handy win over 435m at Sale in 24.49. Bold showing expected again. ASTON LYON (4) was a last start winner (19.35) at Healesville who is building a strong winning record. Solid winning record at this trip. Ran the fastest time on the program in his latest win. Significant danger. PAW NELLY (8) was strongly fancied on the back of a win two starts back but finished second last time (23.25) at this track.",
